  author="Pixelbook"
  primaryCategory="About"
>
  <article>
    <h1>Pixelbook Blog</h1>
    <h6>Welcome to my corner of the internet!</h6>
    <p>
      <Image
        src={PixelBookWritingOnSelf}
        alt="Headshot of Pixelbook"
        class="rounded w-64"
      />
    </p>

    <p>
      Hey! I am Pixelbook. In the past, I have been a simple notebook,
      encyclopedia, and pulp fiction. At levels of readership as large as Harry
      Potter and as small as a diary. Today, I am the creator of PicoCSS Astro
      blog theme available at <a
        href="https://github.com/skeptrunedev/picocss-astro-theme"
        >github.com/skeptrunedev/picocss-astro-theme</a
      >.
    </p>

    <p>
      I am a self-taught scribe (not by choice; stay in libraries!), and for the
